<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="id">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Dashboard Luasan Sawah — Pulau Rote Ndao</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}

:root{

  --bg:#f5f3ee;--surface:#fff;--surface2:#eeece7;--border:rgba(0,0,0,0.08);--border2:rgba(0,0,0,0.15);

  --text:#18180f;--text2:#5a5a50;--text3:#9a9a8a;

  --g50:#eaf3de;--g100:#c0dd97;--g200:#97c459;--g400:#639922;--g600:#3b6d11;--g700:#2d5409;--g800:#1e3a07;

  --t400:#1d9e75;--t600:#0f6e56;--a400:#ba7517;--b400:#378add;--b600:#185fa5;

  --r8:8px;--r12:12px;--r16:16px;

}

@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){

  :root{

    --bg:#101010;--surface:#1a1a16;--surface2:#222218;--border:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);--border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);

    --text:#f0ede5;--text2:#9a9a90;--text3:#555550;

    --g50:#162408;--g100:#2d5409;--g200:#3b6d11;

  }

}

html{font-size:15px;scroll-behavior:smooth}

body{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;line-height:1.5}



/* TOPBAR */

.topbar{background:var(--surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:56px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:1000;backdrop-filter:blur(10px)}

.tb-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}

.tb-icon{width:30px;height:30px;background:var(--g600);border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}

.tb-icon svg{width:16px;height:16px;fill:#fff}

.tb-title{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}

.tb-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);display:block}

.tb-badges{display:flex;gap:5px}

.bdg{font-size:9px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.04em}

.bdg-g{background:var(--g50);color:var(--g700);border-color:var(--g100)}

.bdg-b{background:#e6f1fb;color:var(--b600);border-color:#b5d4f4}

.bdg-r{background:#fcebeb;color:#a32d2d;border-color:#f09595;animation:blink 2s infinite}

@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.5}}



/* LAYOUT */

.main{max-width:1360px;margin:0 auto;padding:1.5rem 1.5rem 4rem}



/* HERO */

.hero{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:1.25rem;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}

.hero h1{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,38px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:3px}

.hero h1 em{font-weight:300;color:var(--g600);font-style:italic}

.hero-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);letter-spacing:.05em}

.upd{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);padding:4px 10px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:20px;display:inline-block}



/* YEAR PANEL */

.year-panel{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:1.1rem 1.4rem;margin-bottom:1.1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem}

.yr-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;white-space:nowrap}

.yr-wrap{flex:1;position:relative}

input[type=range]{-webkit-appearance:none;width:100%;height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--g600) var(--pct,60%),var(--border2) var(--pct,60%));outline:none;cursor:pointer}

input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;width:19px;height:19px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g600);border:3px solid var(--surface);box-shadow:0 0 0 1.5px var(--g400);cursor:pointer;transition:transform .15s}

input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover{transform:scale(1.18)}

.yr-ticks{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:9px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:4px}

.yr-num{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:34px;font-weight:600;color:var(--g600);min-width:76px;text-align:right;line-height:1}

.play-btn{background:var(--g600);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;width:34px;height:34px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:background .2s,transform .1s;flex-shrink:0}

.play-btn:hover{background:var(--g700);transform:scale(1.06)}



/* METRICS */

.metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:1.1rem}

.metric{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:1rem 1.1rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}

.metric:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}

.metric::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%}

.mg::before{background:var(--g600)}.mt::before{background:var(--t400)}.ma::before{background:var(--a400)}.mb::before{background:var(--b400)}

.m-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:5px}

.m-val{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);line-height:1;margin-bottom:2px}

.m-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3)}

.up{color:var(--t600)}.dn{color:#a32d2d}



/* MAP + RANK ROW */

.map-rank-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:1.1rem;margin-bottom:1.1rem}



/* MAP CARD */

.map-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);overflow:hidden;position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column}

.map-card-header{padding:.9rem 1.1rem .6rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}

.card-title{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:500}

.map-legend-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:9px;color:var(--text3)}

.map-legend-bar{width:80px;height:8px;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(to right,#c0dd97,#3b6d11)}

#leaflet-map{flex:1;min-height:340px;border-radius:0}



/* LEAFLET OVERRIDES */

.leaflet-container{background:var(--bg)!important;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}

.leaflet-control-zoom a{font-family:monospace}

.kec-tooltip{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.12);min-width:140px}

.kec-tooltip strong{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:14px;display:block;margin-bottom:2px;color:var(--g600)}

.kec-tooltip .t-ha{font-size:13px;font-weight:500}

.kec-tooltip .t-pct{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3)}

.leaflet-popup-content-wrapper{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r12);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.15);padding:0}

.leaflet-popup-content{margin:0;padding:0}

.leaflet-popup-tip-container{display:none}



/* RANK */

.rank-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:.9rem 1.1rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}

.rank-card .card-title{margin-bottom:.75rem}

.rank-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;overflow-y:auto;max-height:360px}

.rank-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:var(--r8);background:var(--surface2);cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color .18s,background .18s}

.rank-item:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}

.rank-item.active{border-color:var(--g400);background:var(--g50)}

.rank-num{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);min-width:14px;text-align:center}

.rank-info{flex:1;min-width:0}

.rank-name{font-size:11px;color:var(--text);font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}

.rank-bar-track{height:3px;background:var(--border2);border-radius:2px;margin-top:3px}

.rank-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:2px;transition:width .5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}

.rank-ha{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);text-align:right;min-width:64px;line-height:1.4}



/* DETAIL PANEL */

.detail-panel{background:var(--g50);border:1px solid var(--g100);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.1rem;display:none;animation:fadeIn .25s ease}

.detail-panel.show{display:block}

@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

.d-name{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--g800);margin-bottom:2px}

.d-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--g600);margin-bottom:10px}

.d-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);gap:8px}

.d-item label{font-size:9px;color:var(--g600);display:block;margin-bottom:2px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}

.d-item span{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--g800);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}

.d-close{cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;color:var(--g600);text-decoration:underline;margin-top:8px;display:inline-block}



/* CHARTS ROW */

.charts-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1.1rem;margin-bottom:1.1rem}



/* BAR CARD */

.bar-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:.9rem 1.1rem}

.bar-rows{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin-top:.75rem}

.bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}

.bar-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);min-width:108px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}

.bar-track{flex:1;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:3px;height:14px;overflow:hidden}

.bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;transition:width .55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}

.bar-num{font-size:9px;color:var(--text);min-width:60px;text-align:right;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}



/* CHART CARDS */

.chart-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:.9rem 1.1rem}

.chart-wrap{position:relative;width:100%}

.legend-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px}

.lg-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:10px;color:var(--text2)}

.lg-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0}



/* TREND CHART CARD */

.trend-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:.9rem 1.1rem}



/* FOOTER */

.footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:1.1rem;margin-top:.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}

.footer-note{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.7;max-width:680px}

.footer-btns{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-shrink:0}

.sbtn{font-size:10px;padding:6px 13px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid var(--border2);background:var(--surface);color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;transition:background .15s}

.sbtn:hover{background:var(--surface2)}

.sbtn.p{background:var(--g600);color:#fff;border-color:var(--g600)}

.sbtn.p:hover{background:var(--g700)}



@media(max-width:1100px){.map-rank-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}.charts-row{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}

@media(max-width:768px){.metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.charts-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}.d-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.tb-badges{display:none}}

@media(max-width:480px){.metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.year-panel{flex-wrap:wrap}}

</style>

</head>

<body>



<div class="topbar">

  <div class="tb-brand">

    <div class="tb-icon">

      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 14l-5-5 1.41-1.41L12 14.17l7.59-7.59L21 8l-9 9z"/></svg>

    </div>

    <div>

      <div class="tb-title">Sawah Rote Ndao</div>

      <span class="tb-sub">Dashboard Luasan Lahan Pertanian</span>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="tb-badges">

    <span class="bdg bdg-g">GEE · Landsat/Sentinel</span>

    <span class="bdg bdg-b">Shapefile BPS/BIG</span>

    <span class="bdg bdg-r">● Simulasi Data</span>

  </div>

</div>



<div class="main">



  <div class="hero">

    <div>

      <h1>Luasan Sawah<br><em>Pulau Rote Ndao</em></h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">Kabupaten Rote Ndao · Nusa Tenggara Timur · 10 Kecamatan</p>

    </div>

    <span class="upd">Diperbarui: Mei 2026</span>

  </div>



  <!-- YEAR SLIDER -->

  <div class="year-panel">

    <span class="yr-lbl">Tahun</span>

    <div class="yr-wrap">

      <input type="range" id="yearSlider" min="2000" max="2025" value="2024" step="1">

      <div class="yr-ticks"><span>2000</span><span>2005</span><span>2010</span><span>2015</span><span>2020</span><span>2025</span></div>

    </div>

    <div class="yr-num" id="yearDisplay">2024</div>

    <button class="play-btn" id="playBtn" title="Animasi per tahun">▶</button>

  </div>



  <!-- METRICS -->

  <div class="metrics">

    <div class="metric mg"><div class="m-lbl">Total Sawah</div><div class="m-val" id="m-total">—</div><div class="m-sub" id="m-tsub">hektar</div></div>

    <div class="metric mt"><div class="m-lbl">Δ vs Tahun 2000</div><div class="m-val" id="m-chg">—</div><div class="m-sub">hektar bertambah</div></div>

    <div class="metric ma"><div class="m-lbl">Kecamatan Terluas</div><div class="m-val" id="m-top">—</div><div class="m-sub" id="m-tsub2">—</div></div>

    <div class="metric mb"><div class="m-lbl">Cakupan Daratan</div><div class="m-val" id="m-cov">—</div><div class="m-sub">dari 97.854 ha luas pulau</div></div>

  </div>



  <!-- DETAIL PANEL -->

  <div class="detail-panel" id="detailPanel">

    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between">

      <div>

        <div class="d-name" id="dName">—</div>

        <div class="d-sub">Detail kecamatan terpilih</div>

      </div>

      <span class="d-close" onclick="clearSel()">✕ tutup</span>

    </div>

    <div class="d-grid">

      <div class="d-item"><label>Luas Sawah</label><span id="d-ha">—</span></div>

      <div class="d-item"><label>Tadah Hujan</label><span id="d-th">—</span></div>

      <div class="d-item"><label>Irigasi</label><span id="d-ir">—</span></div>

      <div class="d-item"><label>½ Teknis</label><span id="d-ht">—</span></div>

      <div class="d-item"><label>% dari Total</label><span id="d-pct">—</span></div>

      <div class="d-item"><label>Δ vs 2000</label><span id="d-chg">—</span></div>

    </div>

  </div>



  <!-- MAP + RANK -->

  <div class="map-rank-row">

    <div class="map-card">

      <div class="map-card-header">

        <span class="card-title">Peta Choropleth — Luasan Sawah per Kecamatan</span>

        <div class="map-legend-wrap">

          <span>Rendah</span>

          <div class="map-legend-bar"></div>

          <span>Tinggi</span>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div id="leaflet-map"></div>

    </div>

    <div class="rank-card">

      <div class="card-title">Peringkat Kecamatan</div>

      <div class="rank-list" id="rankList"></div>

    </div>

  </div>



  <!-- BAR + CHARTS -->

  <div class="charts-row">

    <div class="bar-card">

      <div class="card-title">Distribusi Luasan per Kecamatan (ha)</div>

      <div class="bar-rows" id="barRows"></div>

    </div>

    <div class="chart-card">

      <div class="card-title">Komposisi Jenis Sawah</div>

      <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:160px;margin-top:.5rem">

        <canvas id="typeChart" role="img" aria-label="Donut chart jenis sawah: tadah hujan 62%, irigasi sederhana 24%, setengah teknis 14%."></canvas>

      </div>

      <div class="legend-row" style="margin-top:10px;justify-content:center">

        <span class="lg-item"><span class="lg-dot" style="background:#3b6d11"></span>Tadah Hujan 62%</span>

        <span class="lg-item"><span class="lg-dot" style="background:#1d9e75"></span>Sederhana 24%</span>

        <span class="lg-item"><span class="lg-dot" style="background:#97c459"></span>½ Teknis 14%</span>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="chart-card">

      <div class="card-title">Pertambahan per Dekade (ha)</div>

      <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:200px;margin-top:.5rem">

        <canvas id="decadeChart" role="img" aria-label="Bar chart pertambahan sawah per dekade."></canvas>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>



  <!-- TREND -->

  <div class="trend-card" style="margin-bottom:1.1rem">

    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:.6rem">

      <span class="card-title">Tren Luas Sawah 2000–2025 (ha)</span>

    </div>

    <div class="legend-row" id="trendLegend"></div>

    <div class="chart-wrap" style="height:200px">

      <canvas id="trendChart" role="img" aria-label="Grafik tren luas sawah 2000 hingga 2025. Total meningkat dari ~9.500 ha menjadi ~13.800 ha."></canvas>

    </div>

  </div>



  <!-- FOOTER -->

  <div class="footer">

    <div class="footer-note">

      <strong style="color:var(--text2)">Sumber Data:</strong> Google Earth Engine (GEE) — citra Landsat 5/7/8/9 &amp; Sentinel-2 MSI ·

      Batas administrasi kecamatan: Shapefile BPS/BIG Kab. Rote Ndao ·

      Metode: NDVI + LSWI thresholding musim tanam padi · Validasi lapangan Dinas Pertanian.<br>

      <em>Data merupakan estimasi simulasi berbasis pola historis untuk keperluan visualisasi. Gunakan script GEE resmi untuk data produksi aktual.</em>

    </div>

    <div class="footer-btns">

      <button class="sbtn" onclick="window.print()">⎙ Cetak</button>

      <button class="sbtn p" onclick="copyLink()">⊕ Salin Link</button>

    </div>

  </div>



</div><!-- /main -->



